text: Ivanovka () is a rural locality (a village) in Partizansky Selsoviet, Meleuzovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 133 as of 2010. There are 4 streets. == Geography == It is located 21 km from Meleuz, 17 km from Daryino. == References == Category:Rural localities in Meleuzovsky District
title: Ivanovka, Meleuzovsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
